reviewText: I would be lying if i said this film was good! truth is this is pure garbage that just blew. I didn't see one thing about it i liked or enjoyed all the same. The only reason i watchws the whole thing was cuz i was curious how it ends and even that wasn't any better. I give this 5 star because i like these weird delusional movies that you just have to see for yourself to decide weather-or-not you're gunna like it or you're just gunna get sick of it. This crap was both for me...
